  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "36 \u0bae\u0ba3\u0bbf \u0ba8\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b90\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Within 36 hours, five people were shot dead - four critically injured",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Nationwide, five people have been shot dead in the last 36 hours today (28) and four more people have been injured in those incidents and are receiving treatment in hospitals.",
        "As two shooting incidents have been reported in Ambalangoda, the police suspect that they may be related to each other. However, no one has been arrested in connection with the incidents till this evening.",
        "Yesterday (27th) night, two persons entered a house in Rathmalana police division, shot and killed a three-wheeler driver and fled. The tricycle driver identified as Charit Umayanga Silva, 30, is a father of two. When he returned home last night after a ride, the armed men who knocked on the door opened the door and opened fire on him and fled.",
        "Yesterday (27th) night, two people died in a shooting at a mortuary in Ambalangodai-Kalagoda area. A visitor to the death house and the owner of the house were thus killed. Unidentified persons on a motorcycle fired and fled.",
        "About 10 hours before the incident was reported, a person named Vasantha de Soyza was shot dead at Ambalangoda village junction. To take revenge for the incident, the police suspect that Vasantha de Soyza party may be behind the shooting at a death house last night.",
        "Saman Rohitha Perera, a member of the underworld group known as Bus Pota, died after being admitted to the hospital in the shooting that took place in front of the Gampaha court complex yesterday (27).",
        "While he was leaving the court with 5 others for a case of manslaughter, unidentified gunmen in a Wagon R opened fire. Four more injured in the incident are undergoing treatment at Gampaha Hospital.",
        "The shooting is suspected to have been carried out by gang leader Kanemulla Sanjeeva, who is believed to be based in Dubai."
      ],
